{"tid":1408484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日佔路佔鐵又可以撚狗啦","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:40:58.000Z","uid":38482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5b5b4339b49054b19b3aa9e1bb5d6a963b8a68d3","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今晚撚完警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日就輪到撚藍絲啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家聽朝佔路/佔鐵時肯撚定有人鬼屌咁嘈<br />\n佢地講野我地要反擊 <br />\n只不過對淺藍深藍都有唔同手法<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你屌完佢對整件事無好處<br />\n倒不如撚下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打擊佢地對建制信任<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n好啲咁諗可能佢地係長睇TVB 唔知發生緊咩事<br />\n而聽日佢地唔會返到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地鳩企冇得走就係文宣最好時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好一有反對意見就屌</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌左佢地乜鳩都唔柒聽 撚唔到狗</span></span><br />\n以下提出針對兩種主要對象文宣手法<br />\n要分出佢係淺藍定深藍用兩三句已經可以<br />\nexample:問下支唔支持元朗白衣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">yes=<span style=\"color: navy;\">深藍</span> no=<span style=\"color: blue;\">淺藍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中立</span></span>/<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">淺藍</span></span>派<br />\nexample:<br />\n警察濫暴（打街坊/爆頭示威者etc。。）<br />\n警黑合作（俾片佢睇 &amp; 何君妖握手）<br />\n抗爭方向（一&amp;二百萬上街和理非失效/612暫緩）<br />\n傳媒偏頗（CCTVB選擇性報導新聞）<br />\n政府消失（林鄭罷工十餘日 講撤回兩字都講唔出）<br />\n因修例有死士（已經死左六個）<br />\netc<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搶佔道德高地</span></span> 令佢地<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">駁唔到</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再spread我地啲思想<br />\n重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以理服人 </span></span><br />\n務求R人過黎 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">R得幾多得幾多</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">深藍</span></span><br />\n用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">道理唔得</span></span>就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無賴文宣</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好係真 (但<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老吹 呃都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>）<br />\nexample:<br />\n葉劉叫派錢（愈多示威 愈多衝突=愈多錢派<br />\n甚至唔投建制=派更多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍾意既可以吹四千蚊係因為佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n警察打人 呃ot收八萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n示威者收錢-&gt;問佢邊度有得收 叫佢一齊join<br />\n外國勢力-&gt;特朗普話我地暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\netc<br />\n總之<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">愈多陰謀論愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n務求<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打擊</span></span>佢地對<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建制</span></span>既信任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一開頭唔好屌人老母住</span></span><br />\n你地見琴日個dc9孝子 <br />\n一俾人講老母就鬼屌咁嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我地咁做白白浪費左文宣既大好機會<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔需要佢即轉立場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但少一個人反對我地<br />\n對面多一個人內訌<br />\n令佢地懷疑自己<br />\n都對我地有利</span></span><br />\n知自己唔易控制情緒既勇武巴絲就唔洗講/加把口了<br />\n幫手護住啲傾緊既巴絲唔好俾藍絲打就ok了<br />\n<br />\n另外想講<br />\n個人意見唔好再直接佔紅隧了<br />\n要佔就佔紅隧個收費站 等車主唔洗錢過海<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302e71db125781601b8b65d8316e2375693a4799","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52dda0cf3a3b0c019b0f8b39ecbc01658833dbd","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf4e798b86bca77309d4539ca3042c2ecc5c7cb","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c45a535be2007c45a42aaee47a63c8beeaaa3c7","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219c05bd7164e858965c7c9f1f3e4c0ab3e09788","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a9417fef447aca72cdd5976bf815126164d743","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5083fa130fa88a9af036b5a13e5ae0d1e16f1c93","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219eba6b55fa034e9221ccfcd3eb2dc86b880cd2","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8182ed476a44605ef41e1f2726ee2a1a611dda5","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dde0a38a50b47f112e6504dae50e4d3f093599","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910fb7ec27587039e47fa5657ba434960357ad58","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279c9a4995a6d5be24c1ecd5a3862c7c2f2a0a56","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94948d65c5bab356a2f7eebdf1dbb854e80b920e","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ff65300e7408e99b39bed30493e0955d838a00","tid":1408484,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}